{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-001", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.1", "text_original": "止，類以行之，說在同。所存與存者，於存與孰存。", "text_normalized": "止，類以行之，說在同。所存與存者，於存與孰存。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-002", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.2", "text_original": "駟異說推，類之難說，在之大小。五行毋常，勝說在宜。", "text_normalized": "駟異說推，類之難說，在之大小。五行毋常，勝說在宜。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-003", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.3", "text_original": "物盡同名，說在二與鬬，子與愛，食與招，白與視，麗與暴，夫與履。", "text_normalized": "物盡同名，說在二與鬬，子與愛，食與招，白與視，麗與暴，夫與履。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-004", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 4, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.4", "text_original": "一，偏棄之，謂而固是也。", "text_normalized": "一，偏棄之，謂而固是也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-005", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 5, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.5", "text_original": "說在因不可偏去而二。", "text_normalized": "說在因不可偏去而二。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-006", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 6, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.6", "text_original": "說在見與俱一，與二廣，與循無欲惡之為益損也。", "text_normalized": "說在見與俱一，與二廣，與循無欲惡之為益損也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-007", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 7, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.7", "text_original": "說在宜不能而不害。", "text_normalized": "說在宜不能而不害。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-008", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 8, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.8", "text_original": "說在害損而不害。", "text_normalized": "說在害損而不害。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-009", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 9, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.9", "text_original": "說在餘異類不吡。", "text_normalized": "說在餘異類不吡。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-010", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 10, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.10", "text_original": "說在量知而不以五路。", "text_normalized": "說在量知而不以五路。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-011", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 11, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.11", "text_original": "說在久偏去莫加少。", "text_normalized": "說在久偏去莫加少。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-012", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 12, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.12", "text_original": "說在故必熱。", "text_normalized": "說在故必熱。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-013", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 13, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.13", "text_original": "說在頓假必誖。", "text_normalized": "說在頓假必誖。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-014", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 14, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.14", "text_original": "說在不然知其所不知。", "text_normalized": "說在不然知其所不知。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-015", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 15, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.15", "text_original": "說在以名取物之所以然，與所以知之，與所以使人知之，不必同。", "text_normalized": "說在以名取物之所以然，與所以知之，與所以使人知之，不必同。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-016", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 16, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.16", "text_original": "說在病無不必待有。", "text_normalized": "說在病無不必待有。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-017", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 17, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.17", "text_original": "說在所謂疑。", "text_normalized": "說在所謂疑。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-018", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 18, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.18", "text_original": "說在逢、循、遇、過。擢慮不疑。", "text_normalized": "說在逢、循、遇、過。擢慮不疑。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-019", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 19, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.19", "text_original": "說在有無合與一，或復否。", "text_normalized": "說在有無合與一，或復否。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-020", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 20, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.20", "text_original": "說在拒且，然不可正，而不害用工。", "text_normalized": "說在拒且，然不可正，而不害用工。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-021", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 21, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.21", "text_original": "說在宜歐物一體也。", "text_normalized": "說在宜歐物一體也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-022", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 22, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.22", "text_original": "說在俱一惟是。均之絕不。", "text_normalized": "說在俱一惟是。均之絕不。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-023", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 23, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.23", "text_original": "說在所均宇或從。", "text_normalized": "說在所均宇或從。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-024", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 24, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.24", "text_original": "說在長宇久，堯之義也，聲於今而處於古，而異時。", "text_normalized": "說在長宇久，堯之義也，聲於今而處於古，而異時。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-025", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 25, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.25", "text_original": "說在所義，二臨鑑而立景，到多而若少。", "text_normalized": "說在所義，二臨鑑而立景，到多而若少。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-026", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 26, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.26", "text_original": "說在寡區狗犬也，而殺狗非殺犬也，可。", "text_normalized": "說在寡區狗犬也，而殺狗非殺犬也，可。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-027", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 27, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.27", "text_original": "說在重鑑位量，一小而易一大，而缶。", "text_normalized": "說在重鑑位量，一小而易一大，而缶。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-028", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 28, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.28", "text_original": "說在中之外，內使殷美。", "text_normalized": "說在中之外，內使殷美。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-029", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 29, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.29", "text_original": "說在使鑑團景，一不堅白。", "text_normalized": "說在使鑑團景，一不堅白。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-030", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 30, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.30", "text_original": "說在荊之大，其沈淺也。", "text_normalized": "說在荊之大，其沈淺也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-031", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 31, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.31", "text_original": "說在具無久，與宇堅白。", "text_normalized": "說在具無久，與宇堅白。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-032", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 32, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.32", "text_original": "說在因以檻為摶，於以為無知也。", "text_normalized": "說在因以檻為摶，於以為無知也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-033", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 33, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.33", "text_original": "說在意。", "text_normalized": "說在意。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-034", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 34, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.34", "text_original": "在諸其所然諸未然，說在於是推之。意未可知，說在可用過仵。", "text_normalized": "在諸其所然諸未然，說在於是推之。意未可知，說在可用過仵。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-035", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 35, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.35", "text_original": "景不徙，說在改為。一少於二，而多於五，說在建位。", "text_normalized": "景不徙，說在改為。一少於二，而多於五，說在建位。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-036", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 36, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.36", "text_original": "景二，說在重。非半弗斫，則不動，說在端。", "text_normalized": "景二，說在重。非半弗斫，則不動，說在端。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-037", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 37, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.37", "text_original": "景倒，在午有端與景長，說在端。可無也，有之而不可去，說在嘗然。", "text_normalized": "景倒，在午有端與景長，說在端。可無也，有之而不可去，說在嘗然。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-038", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 38, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.38", "text_original": "景迎日，說在轉。正而不可擔，說在摶。", "text_normalized": "景迎日，說在轉。正而不可擔，說在摶。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-039", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 39, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.39", "text_original": "景之大小，說在杝正遠近。宇進無近，說在敷。", "text_normalized": "景之大小，說在杝正遠近。宇進無近，說在敷。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-040", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 40, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.40", "text_original": "二，臨鑑而立，景到，多而若少。說在寡區。", "text_normalized": "二，臨鑑而立，景到，多而若少。說在寡區。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-041", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 41, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.41", "text_original": "鑑立，景一小而易，一大而正，說在中之外內。", "text_normalized": "鑑立，景一小而易，一大而正，說在中之外內。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-042", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 42, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.42", "text_original": "鑑團，景一。行脩以久，說在先後。", "text_normalized": "鑑團，景一。行脩以久，說在先後。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-043", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 43, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.43", "text_original": "負而不撓，說在勝。一法者之相與也，盡類，若方之相合也，說在方。", "text_normalized": "負而不撓，說在勝。一法者之相與也，盡類，若方之相合也，說在方。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-044", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 44, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.44", "text_original": "衡而必正，說在得。", "text_normalized": "衡而必正，說在得。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-045", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 45, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.45", "text_original": "挈與收反，說在權。狂舉不可以知異，說在有不可。", "text_normalized": "挈與收反，說在權。狂舉不可以知異，說在有不可。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-046", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 46, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.46", "text_original": "牛馬之非牛，與可之同，說在兼。", "text_normalized": "牛馬之非牛，與可之同，說在兼。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-047", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 47, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.47", "text_original": "倚者不可正，說在梯。循此循此與彼此同，說在異。", "text_normalized": "倚者不可正，說在梯。循此循此與彼此同，說在異。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-048", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 48, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.48", "text_original": "柱之必住，說在廢材。唱和同串，說在功。", "text_normalized": "柱之必住，說在廢材。唱和同串，說在功。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-049", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 49, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.49", "text_original": "買無貴，說在反其賈。聞所不知，若所知，則兩知之，說在告。", "text_normalized": "買無貴，說在反其賈。聞所不知，若所知，則兩知之，說在告。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-050", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 50, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.50", "text_original": "賈宜則售，說在盡。以言為盡誖，誖，說在其言。", "text_normalized": "賈宜則售，說在盡。以言為盡誖，誖，說在其言。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-051", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 51, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.51", "text_original": "無說而懼，說在弗心。唯吾謂非名也則不可，說在反。", "text_normalized": "無說而懼，說在弗心。唯吾謂非名也則不可，說在反。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-052", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 52, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.52", "text_original": "域，過名也，說在實。無窮不害兼，說在盈否。", "text_normalized": "域，過名也，說在實。無窮不害兼，說在盈否。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-053", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 53, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.53", "text_original": "知知之，否之，足用也。誖。說在無以也。不知其數而知其盡也，說在明者。", "text_normalized": "知知之，否之，足用也。誖。說在無以也。不知其數而知其盡也，說在明者。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-054", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 54, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.54", "text_original": "謂辯無勝，必不當，說在辯。不知其所處，不害愛之，說在喪子者。", "text_normalized": "謂辯無勝，必不當，說在辯。不知其所處，不害愛之，說在喪子者。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-055", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 55, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.55", "text_original": "無不讓也，不可，說在殆。仁義之為內外也，罔，說在仵顏。", "text_normalized": "無不讓也，不可，說在殆。仁義之為內外也，罔，說在仵顏。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-056", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 56, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.56", "text_original": "於一有知焉，有不知焉，說在存。學之益也，說在誹者。", "text_normalized": "於一有知焉，有不知焉，說在存。學之益也，說在誹者。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-057", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 57, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.57", "text_original": "有指於二，而不可逃，說在以二參。誹之可否，不以眾寡，說在可非。", "text_normalized": "有指於二，而不可逃，說在以二參。誹之可否，不以眾寡，說在可非。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-058", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 58, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.58", "text_original": "所知而弗能指，說在春也、逃臣、狗犬、貴者。非誹者誖，說在弗非。", "text_normalized": "所知而弗能指，說在春也、逃臣、狗犬、貴者。非誹者誖，說在弗非。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-059", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 59, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.59", "text_original": "知狗而自謂不知犬，過也，說在重。物甚不甚，說在若是。", "text_normalized": "知狗而自謂不知犬，過也，說在重。物甚不甚，說在若是。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-060", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 60, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.60", "text_original": "通意後對，說在不知其誰謂也。取下以求上也，說在澤。", "text_normalized": "通意後對，說在不知其誰謂也。取下以求上也，說在澤。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-061", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii", "source_id": "mozi-032-canon-ii__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 61, "canonical_ref": "墨子 032.61", "text_original": "不是與是同，說在不州。", "text_normalized": "不是與是同，說在不州。", "notes": ""}
